Question: to find the longest pair sum of an array
Approach-> find sort and sum last two elements of given array

class Solution {
    public static int pairsum(int[] arr) {
       
       if(arr.length==1){
           return arr[0];
       }
       Arrays.sort(arr);
       int sum=(arr[arr.length-1])+(arr[arr.length-2]);
       return sum;
    }
}
